extendedInfo.description: Capture the magic of professional learning that advances student performance. At Learning Forward's 2011 Annual Conference, experience learning that transforms teaching and leadership practices. For five days, top educators will challenge and inspire you. More than 350 intensive preconference sessions, concurrent sessions, and roundtables will cover topics including leadership, examining the impact of professional learning, teaching quality, technology, fundamentals of professional learning, equity, and advocacy. Join us in Anaheim and help ensure great teaching for every student every day.
